---
title: Sweet Chili Pork Banh Mi Baguettes Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Tonight’s dinner features our spin on a Vietnamese banh mi sandwich. Quick-cooking, flavorful, and tossed in a sweet Thai chili sauce, thinly sliced pork makes a perfect sandwich-stuffer. It’s piled high with a sesame-dressed green salad plus crunchy almonds, quick pickled carrots and cukes, and loaded into toasty baguettes spread with spicy mayo. Top with crispy fried onions and as much Sriracha as you like, and serve with extra salad and pickles on the side–all this in  just a quick 15 minutes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663131b29eb2c19a07b966eb-3d5837ed.jpeg
